OL,6,FA driver left a pensioner with facial
OL,7,Ffractures after getting out of his car
OL,8,Fand punching him in a road rage
OL,9,Fincident in Nottinghamshire.
OL,11,FTyran Hands, 27, got angry and hit the
OL,12,F77-year-old man when he criticised his
OL,13,Fstandard of driving on May 14 last
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FHe had honked his horn at Hands
OL,17,Fseconds earlier and then overtook him
OL,18,Ffollowing a near collision in
OL,19,FBlidworth.
