OL,6,FUnhappy at the man's response, Hands
OL,7,Fthen proceeded to follow the pensioner
OL,8,Funtil he pulled over in nearby Belle
OL,9,FVue Lane.
OL,11,FDespite his own young child being in
OL,12,Fthe car with him at the time, the 27-
OL,13,Fyear-old charged over to confront the
OL,14,Fother motorist.
OL,16,FAfter verbally abusing the man, who
OL,17,Fremained in his car, Hands then turned
OL,18,Faway and started walking back to his
OL,19,Fown vehicle.
