OL,4,Cwith facial fractures in road rage
OL,6,FAt that point, the elderly man got out
OL,7,Fof his vehicle and tried to take a
OL,8,Fpicture of Hands and his car, which
OL,9,Friled him up even further.
OL,11,FHe then lashed out by punching the
OL,12,Fvulnerable man straight in the face `
OL,13,Fknocking him over and causing his
OL,14,Fhearing aid to fly onto the floor.
OL,16,FThe assault left the pensioner with
OL,17,Fmultiple facial fractures, including
OL,18,Fto his eye socket and his cheek bone.
OL,20,FHands was later charged with causing
OL,21,Fgrievous bodily harm.
