OL,3,CDriver jailed after leaving pensioner
OL,4,Cwith facial fractures in road rage
OL,6,FAppearing at Nottingham Crown Court on
OL,7,Fon Monday (February 26), he pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty.
OL,10,FHands, of Sotherby Drive, Cheltenham,
OL,11,Fwas jailed for one year and eight
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FDetective Constable Chloe Baugh, of
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,17,F"The level of violence and aggression
OL,18,Fdemonstrated by Hands that day was
OL,19,Fdeplorable and completely over the top.
