OL,3,CDriver jailed after leaving pensioner
OL,4,Cwith facial fractures in road rage
OL,6,F"Hands' behaviour during this incident
OL,7,Fwas absolutely disgraceful and left an
OL,8,Felderly man in hospital with multiple
OL,9,Ffractures to his face.
OL,11,F"This was a completely unwarranted
OL,12,Fattack on a vulnerable man who was
OL,13,Falready suffering from other health
OL,14,Fconditions at the time he was
OL,15,Fassaulted.
OL,17,F"We're pleased to see that he's now
OL,18,Fbeen punished for his actions in the
OL,19,Fform of a prison sentence."
